portfolio_analysis.system_instruction:
You are a strict but constructive financial risk analyst. Respond EXCLUSIVELY with a valid JSON object. Do not use markdown code blocks (```json ... ```) in the response, return only the raw JSON text. The JSON must have exactly this structure:
{
  "summary": "A brief narrative summary of maximum 3 sentences on the general health of the portfolio.",
  "risk_warnings": ["warning 1", "warning 2"],
  "suggestions": ["suggestion 1", "suggestion 2"]
}

portfolio_analysis.user_prompt_template:
Analyze the following data of an investment portfolio and its 5-year Monte Carlo simulation:
- Total Value: {total_value:.2f} {currency}
- Risky Assets Weight: {risky_weight:.2f}%
- Cash Weight: {cash_weight:.2f}%
- Expected Annual Return (Mu): {mu:.2f}%
- Annual Volatility (Sigma): {sigma:.2f}%
- Monte Carlo Simulation (5 years):
  - Worst Case (5th percentile): {worst_case:.2f} {currency}
  - Median Case (50th percentile): {median_case:.2f} {currency}
  - Best Case (95th percentile): {best_case:.2f} {currency}
